SIMPLE: profiteer
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: profiteer
<hw>profiteer</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who makes an excessive and
unconscionable profit by exploiting scarcity or a monopoly
position.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>profiteer</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: profiteer
<hw>profiteer</hw> <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To make an excessive profit, as
on the sale of difficult to obtain goods; to act as a
profiteer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Profiting</ent>⟦br⟧
